title: War of the Roses: Did He Photoshop the Results?
description: Carrie recently got an STD and the only person she could have gotten it from was her boyfriend Brad that she's been with for 2 years.  So she thinks he's cheating but he did get tested himself and his results were negative.  Or were they?
